oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Wanda Jackson, Justin Tubb, and Gary Van
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Grand Ole Opry (Radio program); Harry (Hap) Peebles Agency; Jackson, Wanda, 1937-; Tubb, Justin; Van, Gary;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: One color offset printing plate (black on silver) advertising Grand Ole Opry stars Wanda Jackson, Justin Tubb, Alec Houston and Elmer, Gary Van, the Western Caravan, and Mike Post, available through the Harry (Hap) Peebles Agency. The plate features photographs of Wanda Jackson, Justin Tubb, Alec Houston and Elmer, and Gary Van. The plate is double sided, but the images and information are the same on the reverse side.
